{"tid":1041823,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐聯16強對曼聯違規！歐洲足協決定處罰PSG","createTime":"2019-03-01T06:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T13:34:39.000Z","uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"81de41043661373f68855991026a3a90b5c88426","tid":1041823,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"2019年2月12日歐聯16強首回合，巴黎聖日耳門在英格蘭作客對陣曼聯。巴黎聖日耳門因球迷燃放煙花爆竹、投擲物品、損害行為、人群騷亂遭到歐洲足協指控。<br />\n<br />\n  處罰決定：巴黎聖日耳門被罰款4.1萬歐元。法國球會要在30天內與曼聯球會方面取得聯繫，以解決遭到巴黎聖日耳門球迷破壞的隔離網與座位的問題"},{"pid":"f5b7ce8f6a80099ba2166e22ff352d5e026719ca","tid":1041823,"uid":3813,"like":25,"dislike":15,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"虐畜？"},{"pid":"a2ebe80b3da20807f98a0e9316700cc081c6c3e0","tid":1041823,"uid":5475,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"閉門啦屌"},{"pid":"f4a42a0f9ad46557c4ef2a5230f88838fc6ebc40","tid":1041823,"uid":3194,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"虐畜唔使罰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56395ab36151cf7414cc07b45b6632264cea241a","tid":1041823,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"4.1萬 夠唔夠出屁馬一日既人工"},{"pid":"6433fe01e8fceb668bc32d27e8a0cb5c03ca3fbb","tid":1041823,"uid":40588,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"56395ab36151cf7414cc07b45b6632264cea241a","tid":1041823,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"4.1萬 夠唔夠出屁馬一日既人工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"比曼聯用財技滾一滾 4.1萬隨時變4100萬<br />\n<br />\n又可以買個新c朗"},{"pid":"4e7bfa56f78a1e666ff9c9f88a4947dbb1c5b682","tid":1041823,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6433fe01e8fceb668bc32d27e8a0cb5c03ca3